<aside class="buildMenu">
      <div id="manual">
        <p>1) Design your build order:</p>
        <button title="Move up" id="upNdownup">↑</button>
        <button title="Move down" id="upNdowndown">↓</button>
        <button title="Add row" id="createRowBtn">+</button>
        <button title="Delete row" id="deleteRowBtn">x</button>
        <button title="Clear EVERYTHING" id="clearTableBtn">Clear ALL</button>
        <div class="break"></div>
        <p>2) Save your build to URL:</p>
        <button title="Save" id="saveToURLBtn">Save</button>
        <div class="break"></div>
        <p>3) Upload build to the database:</p>
        <input type="hidden" id="scoreU" name="value" value="1">
        <input type="hidden" id="optionsU" name="username" value="">
        <button title="Upload" id="AddDocument_CustomIDBtn">Upload</button>
        <div class="break"></div>
        <p>Drag the icons below to make your build:</p>
      </div>
